1
00:01:34,280 --> 00:01:39,950
[The Story of Xing Fu]

2
00:01:40,050 --> 00:01:42,950
[Episode 34]

3
00:02:02,260 --> 00:02:02,630
Yes,

4
00:02:02,630 --> 00:02:03,020
Xingfu.

5
00:02:03,020 --> 00:02:03,710
What's up?

6
00:02:04,590 --> 00:02:05,300
Where are you?

7
00:02:06,300 --> 00:02:07,100
I'm making dumplings

8
00:02:07,180 --> 00:02:08,380
with Mom back home.

9
00:02:09,380 --> 00:02:09,820
I see.

10
00:02:10,230 --> 00:02:11,100
Wait for me.

11
00:02:11,100 --> 00:02:11,820
I'll be back.

12
00:02:12,710 --> 00:02:13,070
Okay.

13
00:02:13,740 --> 00:02:14,630
See you later.

14
00:02:15,260 --> 00:02:15,790
Mom.

15
00:02:15,990 --> 00:02:16,990
Xingfu will be here soon.

16
00:02:34,910 --> 00:02:35,070
Mom.

17
00:02:35,070 --> 00:02:35,820
Let's make more dumplings.

18
00:02:35,820 --> 00:02:37,070
Then I can pack some back with me.

19
00:02:37,630 --> 00:02:38,100
Okay.

20
00:02:38,100 --> 00:02:39,030
Xingfu can take some too.

21
00:02:39,230 --> 00:02:39,540
Yes.

22
00:02:39,540 --> 00:02:40,540
She can take some too.

23
00:02:43,100 --> 00:02:44,350
She loves

24
00:02:44,580 --> 00:02:45,820
Chinese chives and egg filling.

25
00:02:46,510 --> 00:02:46,950
Xingfu!

26
00:02:46,980 --> 00:02:47,980
Speak of the devil.

27
00:02:48,350 --> 00:02:48,790
Come.

28
00:02:49,070 --> 00:02:50,100
Help me make dumplings.

29
00:02:52,420 --> 00:02:52,980
Come here.

30
00:02:53,750 --> 00:02:54,420
Why?

31
00:02:54,860 --> 00:02:55,580
I have some questions.

32
00:02:56,470 --> 00:02:56,860
Wait.

33
00:03:01,860 --> 00:03:03,820
Did you draft Chuanmei and Xiuyu's contract?

34
00:03:06,660 --> 00:03:07,260
Yes.

35
00:03:08,140 --> 00:03:09,310
Wan Chuanjia asked me to.

36
00:03:12,660 --> 00:03:13,350
He promised...

37
00:03:16,700 --> 00:03:17,100
Xingfu.

38
00:03:17,100 --> 00:03:18,790
Why did you slap me?

39
00:03:19,350 --> 00:03:20,190
I'm their lawyer.

40
00:03:20,190 --> 00:03:21,910
Why can't I draft a contract for them?

41
00:03:21,950 --> 00:03:23,070
Did he promise to give you a lot of money?

42
00:03:25,260 --> 00:03:26,950
Xiuyu studied just as hard as you.

43
00:03:27,510 --> 00:03:29,470
She got accepted into a university
but someone took her spot.

44
00:03:30,540 --> 00:03:31,510
And what did you do?

45
00:03:31,910 --> 00:03:33,260
You drafted that contract for Wan Chuanjia.

46
00:03:33,540 --> 00:03:34,580
Where is your good conscience?

47
00:03:35,190 --> 00:03:36,380
What do you mean?

48
00:03:36,380 --> 00:03:38,070
I didn't commit the deed.

49
00:03:38,310 --> 00:03:39,980
I merely drafted a contract.

50
00:03:40,470 --> 00:03:40,750
I...

51
00:03:40,790 --> 00:03:42,700
If I didn't do it, anyone else would.

52
00:03:42,790 --> 00:03:44,660
You know this contract is null and void.

53
00:03:45,070 --> 00:03:46,100
You're a lawyer.

54
00:03:46,510 --> 00:03:47,660
Why did you draft it?

55
00:03:51,100 --> 00:03:52,030
900,000 yuan?

56
00:03:52,820 --> 00:03:54,030
You are quite bold
to put that number on the contract.

57
00:03:55,230 --> 00:03:56,310
Guan Tao told me this contract

58
00:03:56,310 --> 00:03:57,510
was drafted by a professional.

59
00:03:57,750 --> 00:03:58,750
I knew right away it was you.

60
00:04:01,070 --> 00:04:01,980
He didn't reveal your name

61
00:04:01,980 --> 00:04:03,030
because he cares about my feelings.

62
00:04:03,380 --> 00:04:04,540
Whatever others and Guan Tao say,

63
00:04:04,660 --> 00:04:05,750
you believe them.

64
00:04:05,750 --> 00:04:06,950
You trust everyone else.

65
00:04:06,950 --> 00:04:08,950
Why do you trust outsiders

66
00:04:08,950 --> 00:04:10,230
but not me?

67
00:04:10,260 --> 00:04:10,950
Who's your family

68
00:04:10,950 --> 00:04:11,790
and who's an outsider?

69
00:04:12,860 --> 00:04:14,310
The Wangs still think I'm an outsider

70
00:04:14,540 --> 00:04:15,540
and hide everything from me.

71
00:04:16,580 --> 00:04:17,700
You're my sister

72
00:04:17,980 --> 00:04:19,190
and you want to lie to me forever.

73
00:04:19,190 --> 00:04:19,980
Why would I trust you?

74
00:04:24,350 --> 00:04:25,310
And what's wrong with Guan Tao?

75
00:04:25,580 --> 00:04:26,460
He's a lawyer

76
00:04:26,460 --> 00:04:28,310
but he never exploits anyone.

77
00:04:28,310 --> 00:04:28,950
And you,

78
00:04:30,380 --> 00:04:31,900
you used Xiuyu to earn quick money.

79
00:04:32,430 --> 00:04:33,310
You know,

80
00:04:33,340 --> 00:04:35,020
Xiuyu is in the same situation
like yours from back then.

81
00:04:35,430 --> 00:04:37,510
But you helped Wan Chuanjia to hurt her.

82
00:04:38,140 --> 00:04:39,670
What did I do to her?

83
00:04:40,140 --> 00:04:41,110
It's precisely because I know

84
00:04:41,110 --> 00:04:42,340
she's in the same situation

85
00:04:42,340 --> 00:04:43,110
that I know

86
00:04:43,110 --> 00:04:44,580
what her choices should be.

87
00:04:45,670 --> 00:04:46,380
Xingyun,

88
00:04:47,820 --> 00:04:49,750
what has become of you?

89
00:04:56,990 --> 00:04:57,630
Xingfu.

90
00:04:57,630 --> 00:04:58,900
What's wrong with you two?

91
00:04:59,340 --> 00:05:00,260
Where are you going?

92
00:05:00,380 --> 00:05:01,460
The dumplings are almost ready.

93
00:05:01,460 --> 00:05:02,580
Eat before you leave.

94
00:05:02,870 --> 00:05:03,430
No, thanks.

95
00:05:03,820 --> 00:05:04,430
I'm busy, Mom.

96
00:05:04,430 --> 00:05:05,140
I've got to go.

97
00:05:33,140 --> 00:05:33,900
Mr. Wan.

98
00:05:35,750 --> 00:05:36,430
Mr. Wan.

99
00:05:40,670 --> 00:05:41,260
You're here.

100
00:05:42,950 --> 00:05:43,380
Have a seat.

101
00:05:58,750 --> 00:06:00,750
You gave me this tea last time.

102
00:06:09,550 --> 00:06:10,340
You found out about everything?

103
00:06:13,510 --> 00:06:14,260
Yes.

104
00:06:19,990 --> 00:06:20,750
Truth be told,

105
00:06:22,070 --> 00:06:22,780
nothing is scarier

106
00:06:24,070 --> 00:06:24,900
than you finding out

107
00:06:25,220 --> 00:06:25,820
everything.

108
00:06:26,670 --> 00:06:27,900
When I visited your home last time,

109
00:06:28,780 --> 00:06:30,460
I even left a reminder to your mother-in-law.

110
00:06:36,700 --> 00:06:38,820
You stared at me from the door

111
00:06:41,260 --> 00:06:42,780
and I felt like I was caught.

112
00:06:43,700 --> 00:06:45,140
Then I left with you absentmindedly.

113
00:06:47,700 --> 00:06:48,990
In the end,

114
00:06:50,580 --> 00:06:51,780
you still caught me.

115
00:06:52,870 --> 00:06:53,750
I do fear you.

116
00:07:01,380 --> 00:07:01,820
Mr. Wan.

117
00:07:03,020 --> 00:07:03,900
I'm not afraid of you.

118
00:07:05,460 --> 00:07:06,430
I respect you.

119
00:07:11,430 --> 00:07:12,670
Do you still do?

120
00:07:16,820 --> 00:07:17,630
I don't know.

121
00:07:23,460 --> 00:07:24,140
Xingfu,

122
00:07:25,340 --> 00:07:25,900
you've never

123
00:07:26,820 --> 00:07:28,310
met Chuanmei after you were married

124
00:07:29,780 --> 00:07:30,820
into Wan Village, right?

125
00:07:32,550 --> 00:07:33,260
Yes.

126
00:07:35,780 --> 00:07:36,820
She was afraid of coming back.

127
00:07:38,700 --> 00:07:39,510
She feels

128
00:07:39,750 --> 00:07:40,670
ashamed.

129
00:07:43,700 --> 00:07:45,700
Xiuyu asked me to bring her to a university.

130
00:07:47,900 --> 00:07:48,780
She told me

131
00:07:50,820 --> 00:07:51,780
her life

132
00:07:51,950 --> 00:07:52,990
was stolen.

133
00:07:56,780 --> 00:07:57,630
Chuanmei

134
00:07:57,670 --> 00:07:59,070
hanged herself when she came back last time.

135
00:08:00,950 --> 00:08:03,020
Chuanjia found out in time
so nothing dire happened.

136
00:08:03,990 --> 00:08:05,380
Chuanmei hanged herself?

137
00:08:06,870 --> 00:08:08,260
Why did she do that?

138
00:08:09,340 --> 00:08:10,190
Shame, I guess.

139
00:08:12,700 --> 00:08:14,110
Whenever I close my eyes now,

140
00:08:15,340 --> 00:08:16,110
I can see

141
00:08:16,310 --> 00:08:17,020
the red mark

142
00:08:17,020 --> 00:08:18,900
on her neck.

143
00:08:21,900 --> 00:08:22,870
I'm getting old.

144
00:08:24,820 --> 00:08:26,020
I can't remember the present

145
00:08:26,550 --> 00:08:28,550
but I retain the past very well.

146
00:08:31,670 --> 00:08:32,140
Chuanmei

147
00:08:32,140 --> 00:08:32,700
was raised

148
00:08:32,820 --> 00:08:34,260
by Chuanjia.

149
00:08:34,780 --> 00:08:35,820
Their mother passed away early.

150
00:08:37,510 --> 00:08:38,750
I was busy working with other villagers

151
00:08:38,750 --> 00:08:39,900
to make a living

152
00:08:40,550 --> 00:08:41,700
and was hardly home.

153
00:08:43,390 --> 00:08:44,620
This one time,

154
00:08:45,860 --> 00:08:46,740
the weather was awful.

155
00:08:46,980 --> 00:08:47,860
I went home early.

156
00:08:49,175 --> 00:08:49,815
I told myself

157
00:08:50,605 --> 00:08:51,935
to pick them up at school.

158
00:08:53,190 --> 00:08:54,220
But when I arrived there,

159
00:08:56,030 --> 00:08:57,910
I realized I didn't know which grades they were in.

160
00:09:00,310 --> 00:09:02,190
I failed as a father.

161
00:09:10,270 --> 00:09:11,190
Children are your debts.

162
00:09:18,740 --> 00:09:19,340
Xingfu,

163
00:09:20,910 --> 00:09:22,150
go back and tell Xiuyu

164
00:09:24,030 --> 00:09:25,950
that Wanjia Group
will not stop paying her salary.

165
00:09:26,740 --> 00:09:27,670
It will be paid

166
00:09:28,670 --> 00:09:30,030
from Chuanjia's and my pocket.

167
00:09:30,740 --> 00:09:31,950
If she has any other requests,

168
00:09:32,430 --> 00:09:33,340
feel free to let us know.

169
00:09:37,700 --> 00:09:38,580
Xiuyu said

170
00:09:39,740 --> 00:09:41,070
all she wants is to go to a university.

171
00:09:51,220 --> 00:09:51,700
Mr. Wan.

172
00:09:51,700 --> 00:09:52,310
I have to go now.

173
00:09:53,670 --> 00:09:54,190
Xingfu,

174
00:09:57,070 --> 00:09:57,910
you know everything now.

175
00:09:58,620 --> 00:09:59,500
What do you plan to do?

176
00:09:59,950 --> 00:10:01,390
It's not about what I plan to do.

177
00:10:02,070 --> 00:10:03,620
It's about what Xiuyu plans to do.

178
00:10:08,980 --> 00:10:09,580
Mr. Wan.

179
00:10:11,790 --> 00:10:12,790
I know everything now.

180
00:10:13,670 --> 00:10:14,790
What do you plan to do?

181
00:10:44,460 --> 00:10:45,100
Xiuyu.

182
00:10:45,500 --> 00:10:46,310
You're still awake.

183
00:11:25,950 --> 00:11:26,670
Xiuyu,

184
00:11:28,310 --> 00:11:29,950
I just talked to Mr. Wan.

185
00:11:34,460 --> 00:11:35,270
He told me

186
00:11:35,270 --> 00:11:36,550
that when Chuanmei came back last time,

187
00:11:37,620 --> 00:11:38,910
she tried to hang herself.

188
00:11:40,910 --> 00:11:42,740
Chuanjia found out in time

189
00:11:44,220 --> 00:11:45,220
so she was saved.

190
00:11:47,190 --> 00:11:47,910
What?

191
00:11:51,700 --> 00:11:52,340
She tried to suicide?

192
00:11:57,220 --> 00:11:58,790
She doesn't have the right to.

193
00:12:03,190 --> 00:12:04,580
I'm the victim.

194
00:12:10,070 --> 00:12:11,620
I am the victim.

195
00:12:42,390 --> 00:12:43,100
Xiuyu,

196
00:12:45,100 --> 00:12:46,670
I understand what you're feeling.

197
00:12:50,550 --> 00:12:52,580
I want to defend your right too

198
00:12:52,820 --> 00:12:54,100
but I don't know

199
00:12:54,100 --> 00:12:55,190
how I should proceed.

200
00:12:56,030 --> 00:12:58,460
We can't just force Chuanmei on a path to suicide.

201
00:13:05,390 --> 00:13:06,620
They made a mistake.

202
00:13:07,500 --> 00:13:09,270
They will be hounded by their good conscience.

203
00:13:13,070 --> 00:13:14,390
Chuanmei

204
00:13:14,980 --> 00:13:16,150
will not be able to live happily.

205
00:13:39,310 --> 00:13:39,950
Xiuyu.

206
00:13:39,950 --> 00:13:40,700
Don't cry.

207
00:13:41,270 --> 00:13:41,950
There, there.

208
00:14:10,100 --> 00:14:10,740
Mr. Wan.

209
00:14:10,910 --> 00:14:11,430
You're back.

210
00:14:52,620 --> 00:14:53,220
Xiuyu.

211
00:14:54,460 --> 00:14:55,270
Wake up.

212
00:14:55,820 --> 00:14:56,550
Wake up.

213
00:14:57,070 --> 00:14:58,070
Dad, Mom, and Qinglai

214
00:14:58,070 --> 00:14:59,270
came to visit you.

215
00:15:00,150 --> 00:15:01,500
Your mom even brought you

216
00:15:01,620 --> 00:15:02,910
your favorite toasted flatbreads.

217
00:15:03,340 --> 00:15:04,030
It's warm.

218
00:15:04,620 --> 00:15:05,580
Have some.

219
00:15:12,070 --> 00:15:13,100
I'll put them here.

220
00:15:13,390 --> 00:15:14,430
Remember to eat them.

221
00:15:21,270 --> 00:15:22,030
So?

222
00:15:30,220 --> 00:15:30,950
Let me talk to her.

223
00:15:30,980 --> 00:15:31,390
Don't,

224
00:15:31,390 --> 00:15:31,790
Mom.

225
00:15:32,150 --> 00:15:33,270
Give her more time.

226
00:15:46,860 --> 00:15:47,740
Xiuyu,

227
00:15:48,550 --> 00:15:50,150
I know you're upset.

228
00:15:51,980 --> 00:15:52,980
And I'm with you.

229
00:15:53,220 --> 00:15:54,910
I do not want this to be over just like that.

230
00:15:55,860 --> 00:15:56,950
Sometimes, I get so angry

231
00:15:57,550 --> 00:15:58,100
that I think

232
00:15:58,100 --> 00:15:59,620
it's their fault.

233
00:15:59,860 --> 00:16:00,910
So they should bear

234
00:16:01,390 --> 00:16:02,950
the consequences, no matter how dire they are.

235
00:16:08,500 --> 00:16:09,460
However,

236
00:16:09,860 --> 00:16:10,980
if this went out of control,

237
00:16:11,620 --> 00:16:13,390
we would be indirectly killing Chuanmei.

238
00:16:14,220 --> 00:16:16,270
Would we really feel better that way?

239
00:16:18,270 --> 00:16:19,340
Chuanmei did make a mistake

240
00:16:19,860 --> 00:16:21,070
but it's not serious enough to call for her death.

241
00:16:25,670 --> 00:16:26,820
In my head,

242
00:16:26,820 --> 00:16:28,550
there are two people

243
00:16:29,220 --> 00:16:31,430
arguing non-stop.

244
00:16:31,660 --> 00:16:32,740
It's annoying.

245
00:16:34,830 --> 00:16:35,470
Xiuyu,

246
00:16:35,900 --> 00:16:37,020
do you feel the same way?

247
00:16:40,070 --> 00:16:41,540
Why me?

248
00:16:44,230 --> 00:16:45,660
When I had a misfortune,

249
00:16:45,860 --> 00:16:47,260
I asked myself that question too.

250
00:16:49,950 --> 00:16:50,310
And then,

251
00:16:50,310 --> 00:16:52,070
a voice would ring in my head:

252
00:16:53,710 --> 00:16:55,590
those meant to lift heavy responsibilities

253
00:16:55,950 --> 00:16:57,260
would first endure

254
00:16:57,860 --> 00:16:58,900
the trial of the mind,

255
00:16:58,900 --> 00:16:59,830
and the trial of the body.

256
00:17:00,140 --> 00:17:01,020
When you think that way,

257
00:17:01,070 --> 00:17:02,430
you feel strong enough to overcome everything.

258
00:17:10,990 --> 00:17:11,780
Here you go.

259
00:17:11,950 --> 00:17:12,590
Thank you.

260
00:17:14,100 --> 00:17:14,470
Here.

261
00:17:14,470 --> 00:17:14,870
Thanks.

262
00:17:14,870 --> 00:17:15,340
All right.

263
00:17:15,340 --> 00:17:15,780
Let's go.

264
00:17:16,020 --> 00:17:16,540
Let's go.

265
00:17:16,910 --> 00:17:17,630
Take it.

266
00:17:24,230 --> 00:17:25,190
What else do you want to eat?

267
00:17:26,870 --> 00:17:27,780
Do you want to eat this?

268
00:17:30,390 --> 00:17:30,950
Look.

269
00:17:34,060 --> 00:17:34,740
Xingfu.

270
00:17:35,260 --> 00:17:36,060
Is that you?

271
00:17:36,820 --> 00:17:37,670
Do you remember me?

272
00:17:38,390 --> 00:17:39,060
Cai.

273
00:17:39,390 --> 00:17:40,190
It's been a while.

274
00:17:40,190 --> 00:17:40,910
Hi.

275
00:17:40,950 --> 00:17:41,950
Yes, it's been a while.

276
00:17:42,020 --> 00:17:42,390
How are you?

277
00:17:42,390 --> 00:17:43,020
All good?

278
00:17:43,470 --> 00:17:44,780
Is Qinglai

279
00:17:44,780 --> 00:17:45,390
still working on his plot?

280
00:17:45,670 --> 00:17:46,300
Yes, he is.

281
00:17:46,470 --> 00:17:47,870
I now own an inn.

282
00:17:48,100 --> 00:17:50,020
Qinglai supplies vegetables to my inn

283
00:17:50,020 --> 00:17:51,910
and to all other inns in the village.

284
00:17:52,470 --> 00:17:53,260
Oh,

285
00:17:53,260 --> 00:17:54,230
in Wan Village,

286
00:17:54,230 --> 00:17:55,740
there's a Xingfu Inn.

287
00:17:55,740 --> 00:17:56,390
It's quite famous.

288
00:17:56,580 --> 00:17:57,430
Is it yours?

289
00:17:58,740 --> 00:17:59,710
I knew it.

290
00:17:59,780 --> 00:18:01,150
No wonder it's called Xingfu Inn.

291
00:18:01,300 --> 00:18:02,260
What are you doing now then?

292
00:18:02,300 --> 00:18:03,340
Are you still selling vegetables?

293
00:18:03,670 --> 00:18:04,150
Of course.

294
00:18:04,150 --> 00:18:05,230
How else can I feed myself?

295
00:18:06,150 --> 00:18:06,630
Xingfu,

296
00:18:06,740 --> 00:18:07,670
I have an idea.

297
00:18:07,990 --> 00:18:08,500
You see,

298
00:18:08,820 --> 00:18:10,340
Qinglai is still a farmer.

299
00:18:10,870 --> 00:18:11,710
Let's finish

300
00:18:11,710 --> 00:18:12,390
what didn't work

301
00:18:12,390 --> 00:18:13,100
last time.

302
00:18:13,740 --> 00:18:14,670
Honestly,

303
00:18:14,670 --> 00:18:15,430
Qinglai

304
00:18:15,430 --> 00:18:16,670
is a talented farmer.

305
00:18:17,230 --> 00:18:18,820
And organic vegetables

306
00:18:19,100 --> 00:18:20,500
are all the rage now.

307
00:18:20,870 --> 00:18:21,390
Sure.

308
00:18:21,430 --> 00:18:22,470
I'll let him know

309
00:18:22,470 --> 00:18:23,470
and ask him to contact you.

310
00:18:23,630 --> 00:18:23,990
Sure.

311
00:18:24,020 --> 00:18:25,020
Make sure he calls me, okay?

312
00:18:25,020 --> 00:18:25,470
Okay.

313
00:18:25,670 --> 00:18:26,340
What a chance encounter.

314
00:18:26,390 --> 00:18:27,060
I'll leave you be.

315
00:18:27,190 --> 00:18:27,740
See you.

316
00:18:37,150 --> 00:18:37,740
Dear,

317
00:18:38,630 --> 00:18:40,100
I delivered the vegetables to your kitchen.

318
00:18:40,710 --> 00:18:41,500
I'm just dropping by to see you

319
00:18:41,500 --> 00:18:42,190
and get some water before I go.

320
00:18:42,190 --> 00:18:42,580
Okay?

321
00:18:43,500 --> 00:18:44,540
I was meant to call you

322
00:18:44,540 --> 00:18:45,540
to tell you something.

323
00:18:46,190 --> 00:18:46,740
What?

324
00:18:46,870 --> 00:18:48,100
Do you remember Cai?

325
00:18:49,870 --> 00:18:51,020
Of course.

326
00:18:51,780 --> 00:18:53,740
I ran into him in the wet market today.

327
00:18:54,190 --> 00:18:55,020
He told me

328
00:18:55,020 --> 00:18:56,060
he wanted to finish

329
00:18:56,060 --> 00:18:57,470
the failed project.

330
00:18:57,870 --> 00:18:59,020
He wanted you to contact him soon.

331
00:19:00,950 --> 00:19:01,580
Really?

332
00:19:02,430 --> 00:19:03,470
He still wants to establish a special counter?

333
00:19:03,470 --> 00:19:03,990
Yes.

334
00:19:03,990 --> 00:19:05,020
He heard how good

335
00:19:05,020 --> 00:19:06,230
your products are

336
00:19:06,630 --> 00:19:07,540
and wanted to work with you too.

337
00:19:08,820 --> 00:19:09,020
Isn't this great news?

338
00:19:10,020 --> 00:19:11,060
But first thing first,

339
00:19:11,230 --> 00:19:12,670
if you guys strike a deal,

340
00:19:12,870 --> 00:19:15,100
my inn's vegetable supply still takes priority.

341
00:19:16,100 --> 00:19:17,260
Of course.

342
00:19:18,820 --> 00:19:19,670
A special counter...

343
00:19:20,630 --> 00:19:21,390
I need

344
00:19:21,390 --> 00:19:22,230
to expand

345
00:19:22,230 --> 00:19:23,060
and hire more people.

346
00:19:24,820 --> 00:19:26,340
I didn't expect organic vegetables

347
00:19:26,470 --> 00:19:27,470
to be this popular.

348
00:19:27,500 --> 00:19:28,230
Right?

349
00:19:30,020 --> 00:19:31,190
I'll contact him now.

350
00:19:31,950 --> 00:19:32,500
Go.

351
00:19:33,230 --> 00:19:33,740
See you then.

352
00:19:33,950 --> 00:19:34,540
I'll leave you be.

353
00:19:41,150 --> 00:19:41,740
Ms. He.

354
00:19:41,740 --> 00:19:42,300
Hi.

355
00:19:44,820 --> 00:19:45,470
I'm Liu,

356
00:19:45,470 --> 00:19:47,300
a teacher from a school in the town center.

357
00:19:47,540 --> 00:19:48,230
I need a favor

358
00:19:48,260 --> 00:19:49,340
from you.

359
00:19:49,580 --> 00:19:50,260
May I know

360
00:19:50,260 --> 00:19:50,950
if you're free now?

361
00:19:51,540 --> 00:19:52,150
Of course.

362
00:19:53,300 --> 00:19:53,990
Have a seat.

363
00:19:54,470 --> 00:19:55,020
Thank you.

364
00:19:56,020 --> 00:19:57,060
So what is it?

365
00:19:58,870 --> 00:19:59,500
Ms. He.

366
00:20:00,260 --> 00:20:00,870
Actually,

367
00:20:00,990 --> 00:20:02,230
I heard about you long ago.

368
00:20:02,740 --> 00:20:03,630
Did you

369
00:20:03,630 --> 00:20:05,300
work in a big law firm

370
00:20:05,300 --> 00:20:05,950
in the city before?

371
00:20:06,430 --> 00:20:07,020
Yes, I did.

372
00:20:07,710 --> 00:20:08,500
I need

373
00:20:08,500 --> 00:20:09,230
your help.

374
00:20:09,470 --> 00:20:10,580
I need

375
00:20:10,580 --> 00:20:11,580
the expertise

376
00:20:11,580 --> 00:20:12,260
of a lawyer.

377
00:20:12,540 --> 00:20:13,230
Can you

378
00:20:13,230 --> 00:20:14,190
show me the way?

379
00:20:14,910 --> 00:20:15,710
What happened?

380
00:20:16,710 --> 00:20:17,260
You see.

381
00:20:17,670 --> 00:20:18,710
I have several students

382
00:20:19,060 --> 00:20:19,950
who live

383
00:20:20,150 --> 00:20:20,780
in Shuiwei Village

384
00:20:20,780 --> 00:20:21,580
by the foot of the mountain.

385
00:20:22,670 --> 00:20:23,430
They kept falling ill

386
00:20:23,820 --> 00:20:25,300
recently.

387
00:20:25,990 --> 00:20:26,950
It's always

388
00:20:27,230 --> 00:20:28,020
a cold,

389
00:20:28,020 --> 00:20:28,820
a fever,

390
00:20:28,820 --> 00:20:29,500
or diarrhea.

391
00:20:29,780 --> 00:20:30,780
It's been like that for a while.

392
00:20:31,990 --> 00:20:33,740
Why do you need a lawyer for sick students?

393
00:20:35,060 --> 00:20:37,100
Because I think something is not right.

394
00:20:38,910 --> 00:20:40,060
What do you mean?

395
00:20:40,190 --> 00:20:41,390
Hear me out.

396
00:20:41,780 --> 00:20:42,260
Shuiwei Village

397
00:20:42,260 --> 00:20:43,260
is located

398
00:20:43,540 --> 00:20:44,100
downstream

399
00:20:44,100 --> 00:20:45,300
of the Fushui River.

400
00:20:45,820 --> 00:20:47,870
The wastewater treatment plant
of Wanjia Health Products Factory

401
00:20:48,100 --> 00:20:49,670
is located upstream.

402
00:20:50,150 --> 00:20:51,500
After it went

403
00:20:51,500 --> 00:20:52,670
fully operational,

404
00:20:52,670 --> 00:20:53,340
the children

405
00:20:53,710 --> 00:20:55,230
have been falling ill.

406
00:20:55,780 --> 00:20:56,870
I suspect

407
00:20:57,430 --> 00:20:59,230
that they polluted the water.

408
00:20:59,910 --> 00:21:00,470
I confronted them

409
00:21:00,470 --> 00:21:01,470
many times

410
00:21:01,630 --> 00:21:02,710
but they denied it categorically.

411
00:21:03,020 --> 00:21:03,740
They told me

412
00:21:03,990 --> 00:21:04,580
the wastewater

413
00:21:04,580 --> 00:21:05,780
has been properly dealt with.

414
00:21:06,340 --> 00:21:07,430
It is.

415
00:21:07,820 --> 00:21:09,780
Their wastewater treatment plant

416
00:21:09,990 --> 00:21:10,670
occupies part of my land.

417
00:21:10,670 --> 00:21:11,540
So I know.

418
00:21:11,780 --> 00:21:13,020
But the fact

419
00:21:13,430 --> 00:21:15,020
is that those children kept falling ill.

420
00:21:16,390 --> 00:21:17,100
Also,

421
00:21:17,540 --> 00:21:18,540
when they say they have processed the water,

422
00:21:18,820 --> 00:21:20,020
are they telling the truth?

423
00:21:26,230 --> 00:21:26,950
Ms. He.

424
00:21:27,260 --> 00:21:27,950
Truth be told,

425
00:21:28,540 --> 00:21:30,340
I spend most of my time with kids.

426
00:21:31,580 --> 00:21:32,500
The oldest ones

427
00:21:32,630 --> 00:21:33,740
are like 12 or 13 years old

428
00:21:34,500 --> 00:21:35,020
and the youngest ones

429
00:21:35,020 --> 00:21:36,470
are only 7 or 8 years old.

430
00:21:36,740 --> 00:21:38,740
Their life has just begun.

431
00:21:41,060 --> 00:21:41,910
I heard

432
00:21:41,990 --> 00:21:43,950
you know a lawyer called Guan Tao.

433
00:21:45,060 --> 00:21:46,390
He's a famous figure in the villages

434
00:21:46,390 --> 00:21:47,260
nearby.

435
00:21:47,580 --> 00:21:48,580
Everyone calls him

436
00:21:49,340 --> 00:21:50,340
the Village Lawyer.

437
00:21:51,260 --> 00:21:53,340
I want to go to him

438
00:21:53,340 --> 00:21:54,540
to consult him

439
00:21:54,710 --> 00:21:55,710
and see

440
00:21:55,950 --> 00:21:57,430
if there's a solution to this matter.

441
00:22:01,500 --> 00:22:02,230
Sure.

442
00:22:03,470 --> 00:22:04,740
I'll bring you to him tomorrow.

443
00:22:05,990 --> 00:22:06,990
He's a kind person.

444
00:22:07,260 --> 00:22:09,260
He's a lawyer who truly has
the villagers' interests at heart.

445
00:22:09,710 --> 00:22:10,260
Thank you.

446
00:22:11,500 --> 00:22:11,990
(You see,)

447
00:22:11,990 --> 00:22:12,670
(Mr. Liu.)

448
00:22:13,020 --> 00:22:14,990
What makes you think

449
00:22:15,340 --> 00:22:17,190
the wastewater
from the health products factory

450
00:22:17,630 --> 00:22:19,150
caused the children to fall ill?

451
00:22:20,150 --> 00:22:21,190
Do you have any proof?

452
00:22:23,710 --> 00:22:24,990
I don't have

453
00:22:25,470 --> 00:22:26,230
any solid evidence.

454
00:22:26,500 --> 00:22:27,710
But this phenomenon

455
00:22:28,020 --> 00:22:29,580
appeared

456
00:22:29,670 --> 00:22:31,670
after the health products factory

457
00:22:31,670 --> 00:22:32,500
went fully operational.

458
00:22:33,100 --> 00:22:33,950
Don't you think

459
00:22:34,190 --> 00:22:35,630
the timeline matches up?

460
00:22:36,100 --> 00:22:37,990
Has anyone from the village tested

461
00:22:37,990 --> 00:22:38,950
the drinkable water?

462
00:22:39,100 --> 00:22:40,060
Do you know?

463
00:22:40,910 --> 00:22:41,870
I did

464
00:22:41,870 --> 00:22:43,150
talk to the chief of Shuiwei Village.

465
00:22:43,710 --> 00:22:44,470
He said

466
00:22:44,740 --> 00:22:45,500
National Health
and Family Planning Commission

467
00:22:45,500 --> 00:22:46,390
would evaluate

468
00:22:47,060 --> 00:22:47,540
the potable water

469
00:22:47,540 --> 00:22:48,500
in the village

470
00:22:48,500 --> 00:22:49,430
every few months.

471
00:22:50,020 --> 00:22:50,670
No problem

472
00:22:51,150 --> 00:22:52,060
came to light.

473
00:22:52,430 --> 00:22:53,430
Is it possible

474
00:22:53,430 --> 00:22:54,670
that there's another source of pollution?

475
00:22:54,670 --> 00:22:55,740
For example,

476
00:22:55,870 --> 00:22:57,470
is there another factory nearby

477
00:22:57,990 --> 00:22:59,020
or perhaps

478
00:22:59,670 --> 00:23:00,500
it's in your rice,

479
00:23:00,710 --> 00:23:01,230
your noodles,

480
00:23:01,710 --> 00:23:02,230
your vegetables,

481
00:23:02,230 --> 00:23:03,430
or your fruits?

482
00:23:04,020 --> 00:23:05,430
I did notify the Town Council

483
00:23:05,780 --> 00:23:07,260
and they have sent people to investigate.

484
00:23:08,300 --> 00:23:09,230
But nothing

485
00:23:09,470 --> 00:23:10,580
was found.

486
00:23:10,950 --> 00:23:11,630
Mr. Guan.

487
00:23:11,820 --> 00:23:13,150
I'm just

488
00:23:13,390 --> 00:23:14,580
an elementary school teacher.

489
00:23:15,190 --> 00:23:15,910
I might be

490
00:23:15,910 --> 00:23:16,710
overstepping

491
00:23:16,910 --> 00:23:17,780
the bounds here.

492
00:23:18,470 --> 00:23:19,060
But

493
00:23:19,060 --> 00:23:19,740
I spend

494
00:23:19,990 --> 00:23:20,910
every day

495
00:23:21,230 --> 00:23:22,060
with the kids.

496
00:23:22,780 --> 00:23:24,580
I want them to be healthy.

497
00:23:25,100 --> 00:23:26,020
When I see them sick,

498
00:23:26,470 --> 00:23:27,950
it hurts my soul.

499
00:23:28,950 --> 00:23:29,630
Also,

500
00:23:30,780 --> 00:23:31,580
they are not

501
00:23:31,670 --> 00:23:32,740
from a wealthy background.

502
00:23:33,390 --> 00:23:34,630
To treat their kids,

503
00:23:34,990 --> 00:23:35,580
the parents

504
00:23:35,780 --> 00:23:36,190
are so worried

505
00:23:36,190 --> 00:23:37,390
that they can barely eat or sleep.

506
00:23:38,100 --> 00:23:39,670
Knowing how obedient the children are,

507
00:23:39,820 --> 00:23:41,340
I truly feel sorry for them.

508
00:23:42,020 --> 00:23:42,670
So

509
00:23:42,710 --> 00:23:43,500
Mr. Guan,

510
00:23:45,150 --> 00:23:46,100
I came to you

511
00:23:46,950 --> 00:23:47,870
because I believe

512
00:23:47,950 --> 00:23:48,870
you know more than I do.

513
00:23:49,500 --> 00:23:50,820
Can you tell me

514
00:23:51,430 --> 00:23:52,670
if there's a way

515
00:23:53,150 --> 00:23:54,230
to get to the bottom

516
00:23:54,300 --> 00:23:55,390
of this?

517
00:23:56,630 --> 00:23:57,190
Mr. Liu.

518
00:23:57,470 --> 00:23:59,100
How many children in your school manifest

519
00:23:59,190 --> 00:24:00,020
similar syndromes?

520
00:24:01,870 --> 00:24:02,950
Around

521
00:24:03,580 --> 00:24:04,470
eight.

522
00:24:05,540 --> 00:24:06,580
Another three

523
00:24:06,740 --> 00:24:07,740
aren't as affected.

524
00:24:07,990 --> 00:24:09,230
And all those eight students

525
00:24:09,670 --> 00:24:10,870
are from Shuiwei Village?

526
00:24:13,300 --> 00:24:14,780
Do they share anything else

527
00:24:14,780 --> 00:24:15,540
in common?

528
00:24:16,340 --> 00:24:18,100
Anything else

529
00:24:18,390 --> 00:24:19,060
in common...

530
00:24:21,020 --> 00:24:21,580
Right.

531
00:24:22,580 --> 00:24:23,100
They live

532
00:24:23,100 --> 00:24:24,740
near the village border,

533
00:24:24,740 --> 00:24:25,820
next to the river.

534
00:24:26,990 --> 00:24:28,150
When I do my house visits,

535
00:24:28,230 --> 00:24:28,710
I will visit

536
00:24:28,710 --> 00:24:30,060
the ones in the village center

537
00:24:30,470 --> 00:24:31,470
before

538
00:24:31,670 --> 00:24:32,260
visiting

539
00:24:32,260 --> 00:24:33,100
their houses.

540
00:24:34,100 --> 00:24:34,630
I see.

541
00:24:34,670 --> 00:24:35,340
Mr. Liu.

542
00:24:35,540 --> 00:24:36,464
I know someone
from Environment Monitoring Station

543
00:24:36,464 --> 00:24:37,260
in the Ministry of Ecology and Environment.

544
00:24:37,540 --> 00:24:38,870
I'll give you her contact.

545
00:24:39,300 --> 00:24:39,710
You...

546
00:24:39,710 --> 00:24:41,430
You can inform the leader

547
00:24:41,430 --> 00:24:42,150
of Shuiwei Villager.

548
00:24:42,580 --> 00:24:43,190
Okay.

549
00:24:43,740 --> 00:24:44,870
I'm close to the leader.

550
00:24:44,950 --> 00:24:45,500
Just leave the contact

551
00:24:45,580 --> 00:24:46,390
to me later.

552
00:24:46,500 --> 00:24:47,190
I'll talk to him.

553
00:24:48,670 --> 00:24:49,300
Mr. Liu.

554
00:24:50,020 --> 00:24:50,910
Do not

555
00:24:51,470 --> 00:24:52,430
worry about this too much.

556
00:24:52,780 --> 00:24:54,740
My colleagues and I will devise

557
00:24:54,740 --> 00:24:55,710
a plan as soon as possible.

558
00:24:56,430 --> 00:24:57,710
Our sole objective

559
00:24:57,990 --> 00:24:59,870
is to investigate the problem

560
00:24:59,910 --> 00:25:00,710
and solve it.

561
00:25:00,870 --> 00:25:01,300
Thank you

562
00:25:01,300 --> 00:25:02,260
so much.

563
00:25:02,910 --> 00:25:03,470
Sorry

564
00:25:03,470 --> 00:25:03,950
for taking up

565
00:25:03,950 --> 00:25:05,190
so much of your time.

566
00:25:05,500 --> 00:25:07,950
I do not know how else

567
00:25:08,230 --> 00:25:08,710
to express my gratitude.

568
00:25:08,710 --> 00:25:09,150
So...

569
00:25:09,150 --> 00:25:09,990
Thank you.

570
00:25:09,990 --> 00:25:10,340
No worries.

571
00:25:10,340 --> 00:25:10,910
It's my job.

572
00:25:11,540 --> 00:25:12,060
Then,

573
00:25:12,150 --> 00:25:12,820
I shall take my leave.

574
00:25:12,870 --> 00:25:13,390
Okay.

575
00:25:13,990 --> 00:25:14,470
Thank you.

576
00:25:14,870 --> 00:25:15,670
Thanks, Guan.

577
00:25:15,710 --> 00:25:16,340
No worries.

578
00:25:16,470 --> 00:25:16,910
Let's go.

579
00:25:16,910 --> 00:25:17,340
Okay.

580
00:25:17,740 --> 00:25:18,540
Let's go, Mr. Liu.

581
00:25:19,949 --> 00:25:21,780
[Fangyuan Law Firm]

582
00:25:21,780 --> 00:25:22,540
No need to see me out.

583
00:25:22,580 --> 00:25:23,060
Okay.

584
00:25:23,390 --> 00:25:23,910
Bye.

585
00:25:23,910 --> 00:25:24,780
We can walk ourselves out, Guan.

586
00:25:24,870 --> 00:25:25,260
Bye.

587
00:25:25,260 --> 00:25:25,910
All right.

588
00:25:26,260 --> 00:25:26,910
Bye.

