00:25:33,950 --> 00:25:35,150
I'll be frank.

590
00:25:35,990 --> 00:25:36,910
Merging Shuiwei Village

591
00:25:37,580 --> 00:25:38,710
into Wan Village

592
00:25:39,340 --> 00:25:40,910
is like a charity project.

